===Proper Noun===
'''New York'''
# ''(also [[New York State]]):'' A {{USstate}}  Capital: [[Albany]].
# ''(also [[New York City]]):'' The largest city in New York State.  Originally the capital of the United States of America.  Also known as ''New York, New York'' or ''NY, NY'' meaning New York City in New York State.  The city is broken down into five [[boroughs]]:
#:[[Manhattan]]
#:[[Bronx]] ''The Bronx''
#:[[Brooklyn]] ''Kings County''
#:[[Queens]] ''Queens County''
#:[[Staten Island]]

